高于该值',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(17,'credit.level_a_min_score','80','INT','CREDIT','A级最低分','达到该分数视为A级',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(18,'credit.level_b_min_score','50','INT','CREDIT','B级最低分','达到该分数视为B级',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(19,'credit.level_a_advance_hours','24','INT','CREDIT','A级可提前预约时长','单位：小时',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(20,'credit.level_b_advance_hours','12','INT','CREDIT','B级可提前预约时长','单位：小时',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(21,'credit.level_c_advance_hours','6','INT','CREDIT','C级可提前预约时长','单位：小时',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(22,'ui.reservation_start_time','07:00:00','TIME','UI','预约开始时间','前端可选开始时间',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(23,'ui.reservation_end_time','22:30:00','TIME','UI','预约结束时间','前端可选结束时间',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05'),(24,'ui.reservation_step_minutes','30','INT','UI','时间步长','前端时间选择步长',1,'2026-04-25 19:42:05','2026-04-25 19:42:05');
